{"word":"G1690 - ἐμβριμάομαι - embrimáomai - em-brim-ah'-om-ahee - Straitly charge","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἐμβριμάομαι</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>embrimáomai"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>em-brim-ah'-om-ahee"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Straitly charge"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - கண்டிப்பாய்க் கட்டளையிடு, கண்டிப்பாய் சொல்லு"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"1. to snort in (of horses)"},{"paragraph":"2. to be very angry, to be moved with indignation"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> From <a href=\"#/G1722 - ἐν - en - en/1722\">G1722</a> and <b>&#x03B2;&#x03C1;&#x03B9;&#x03BC;&#x03B1;&#x0301;&#x03BF;&#x03BC;&#x03B1;&#x03B9;</b> <b>brimaomai</b> (to <i>snort</i> with anger); to have <i>indignation on</i>, that is, (transitively) to <i>blame</i>, (intransitively) to <i>sigh</i> with chagrin, (specifically) to sternly <i>enjoin:</i> - straitly charge, groan, murmur against."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"}]}